content: Freytes: Merged 4 significant plugin-related PRs this week (#2679, #2678, #2660, #2656) with massive code additions totaling over 729,000 lines, primarily focused on music generation capabilities with Suno and Udio integrations for Eliza. Has 2 open PRs in progress (#2538, #2537) for Reddit client and Truth Social plugin development, showing a concentrated effort on expanding platform integrations. Active on just 2 days but made substantial contributions, with most changes (71%) focused on other work rather than direct feature development.
